 <p style="margin-left: 8; margin-right: 8"><b><font face="Verdana" size="3" color="#DDDD00">Player Feedback on The Bazaar</font><font color="#DDDD00"><br>
      </font>
      </b><font face="Arial" size="2"><font color="#FFC164"><small>8:29 EST - <a href="mailto:hermana@gameznet.com">Hermana</a></small></font><br>
      <br><blockquote>"I like the new features of the Bazaar but there are a few things I would like noted and changed before it goes to the live servers, these may just be bugs but not sure. <br><br>1. I  think it needs a way to limit the returns you get when you search for things (every time I search for <br>things and get big returns my game crashes to the desktop). <br><br>2.I haven't be able to search for things by name, I type in what I want and even if I know a character has what I want it will return nothing.<br>                       <br>Thanks for you time,<br>Very Happy Everquest Player</blockquote></font></p>
